&lt;p&gt;At first glance, it looks like the SSTableReader is trying to load the read meter even though it shouldn&apos;t (or doesn&apos;t need to).  Assigning to Benedict since this seems to be most related to SSTableReader management.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
